    "headline": "Authentic Louisiana Red Beans and Rice",
    "name": "Authentic Louisiana Red Beans and Rice",
    "description": "This easy authentic Louisiana red beans and rice recipe features Cajun seasoning and andouille sausage for hearty, comforting flavor.",
